<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="justice-n">justice <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'dʒʌstɪs/    美 /'dʒʌstɪs/  </p>
<p>[U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>正义；公正；公道 ：</strong></h4>
<p>反 injustice </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a strong sense of justice 
强烈的正义感</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>treat sb with justice 
公平对待某人</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>法律制裁；司法：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Justice has long arms. 
天网恢恢，疏而不漏。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="do-justice-to">do justice to</h3>
<p>1.<strong>恰当处理；公平对待</strong>  </p></div>